sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Client
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Envoy Gateway<br/>443/TCP TLS Terminate
    participant EnvoyFilter as EnvoyFilter<br/>ext_authz
    participant AuthProxy as kube-auth-proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuth as OAuth/OIDC Provider<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS
    participant Upstream as Upstream Component<br/>(via HTTPRoute)

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 1: Platform Ingress Authentication (Gateway API)

    User->>Router: HTTPS/443 (TLS 1.2+)
    Router->>Gateway: HTTPS/443 (TLS termination)
    Gateway->>EnvoyFilter: Internal ext_authz check
    EnvoyFilter->>AuthProxy: HTTPS/8443 (Bearer Token check)
    AuthProxy->>OAuth: HTTPS/443 (OAuth2 client credentials)
    OAuth-->>AuthProxy: Token validation response
    AuthProxy->>K8sAPI: HTTPS/443 (TokenReview, SA token)
    K8sAPI-->>AuthProxy: TokenReview result
    AuthProxy-->>EnvoyFilter: Auth decision
    EnvoyFilter-->>Gateway: Authorized
    Gateway->>Upstream: HTTP/HTTPS (forwarded auth headers)
    Upstream-->>Gateway: Response
    Gateway-->>Router: Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 2: Component Deployment via DataScienceCluster

    participant Admin as Platform Admin
    participant Webhook as DSC Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS
    participant DSCCtrl as DSC Controller
    participant CompCtrl as Component Controller
    participant Manifests as Kustomize Manifests<br/>/opt/manifests-template

    Admin->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply DSC (HTTPS/443, Bearer Token)
    K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validation (HTTPS/9443, mTLS)
    Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Admitted
    K8sAPI-->>Admin: DSC created
    K8sAPI->>DSCCtrl: Watch event (DSC CR)
    DSCCtrl->>K8sAPI: Create component CRs (e.g., Dashboard)
    K8sAPI->>CompCtrl: Watch event (Component CR)
    CompCtrl->>Manifests: Read kustomize manifests
    Manifests-->>CompCtrl: Rendered manifests
    CompCtrl->>K8sAPI: Apply manifests (HTTPS/443, SA Bearer Token)
    K8sAPI-->>CompCtrl: Resources created

    Note over User,Upstream: Flow 3: Monitoring Metrics Collection

    participant OTel as OpenTelemetry Collector<br/>(TargetAllocator)
    participant CompPods as Component Pods<br/>(monitoring label)
    participant Prometheus as MonitoringStack<br/>(Prometheus)
    participant Thanos as ThanosQuerier<br/>10901/TCP gRPC
    participant NSProxy as Namespace Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Dashboard as Dashboard/Client

    OTel->>CompPods: Scrape metrics (HTTP, varies)
    CompPods-->>OTel: Metrics
    OTel->>Prometheus: OTLP HTTP/4318 (TLS)
    Dashboard->>NSProxy: HTTPS/8443 (Bearer Token)
    NSProxy->>NSProxy: kube-rbac-proxy SubjectAccessReview
    NSProxy->>Prometheus: HTTPS/9090 (service-CA TLS)
    Prometheus-->>NSProxy: Metrics data
    NSProxy-->>Dashboard: Metrics response
    Thanos->>Prometheus: gRPC/10901 (TLS, federated query)
    Prometheus-->>Thanos: Query results
